text: Timothy Danladi (born 15 October 1996) is a Nigerian international footballer who plays for Katsina United, as a defender. ==Career== He has played club football for Katsina United. He made his international debut for Nigeria in 2018. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Nigerian footballers Category:Nigeria international footballers Category:Katsina United F.C. players Category:Association football defenders
